<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate.ejs") %>
<div class="privacy-page">

    <div class="privacy-header">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Your privacy matters to us at WanderLust.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-container">

        <div class="policy-card">
            <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
            <p>
                When you use WanderLust, we may collect personal information such as your
                name, email address, and account details. This information helps us
                provide better booking services and improve the platform experience.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-card">
            <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <p>
                The information collected is used to manage bookings, improve the
                website experience, provide customer support, and ensure platform
                security.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-card">
            <h3>3. Data Protection</h3>
            <p>
                WanderLust takes appropriate security measures to protect your data
                from unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-card">
            <h3>4. Third-Party Services</h3>
            <p>
                Some services on WanderLust may use trusted third-party providers
                for payment processing, analytics, or hosting services.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-card">
            <h3>5. User Rights</h3>
            <p>
                Users have the right to access, modify, or request deletion of their
                personal information from our system.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-card">
            <h3>6. Policy Updates</h3>
            <p>
                WanderLust may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect
                improvements or legal requirements.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-card">
            <h3>7. Contact Information</h3>
            <p>
                If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us
                through the WanderLust Contact page.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

</div>